@node Main "X_Lights - Documentation"

                             'X_Lights' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'X_Lights' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} featuring an 'X'-shaped board filled with
light bulbs that are either turned on or off. The @{" goal of the game " link play} is to
turn on all the light bulbs on that board. When you complete a game level,
X_Lights displays a new, more difficult level, and so on.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
               @{"          History          " link histo}
